article.headline: Anderson's 25 lead Lamar over Nicholls State 78-76 in OT
article.description: — Terry Anderson had 25 points in Lamar's 78-76 overtime victory against Nicholls on Saturday night.
article.linkText: Anderson's 25 lead Lamar over Nicholls State 78-76 in OT
article.story: THIBODAUX, La. -- — Terry Anderson had 25 points in Lamar's 78-76 overtime victory against Nicholls on Saturday night. Anderson also added three steals and three blocks for the Cardinals (9-7, 3-0 Southland Conference). His 3-pointer with 4 minutes left in overtime gave the Cardinals the lead for good. Chris Pryor scored 15 points and added six assists. Robert Brown III led the Colonels (7-9, 2-1) with 25 points and Jalen White added 19 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
